comments.text:
+Soy Sauce Minge Explosion I guess you're right there. I did think of 
that, but I guessed I dismissed it.

Although I do agree that what made it funny was that she was crazy 
(which had nothing to do with her gender identity), but I do think that the 
transwoman theme is also played off slightly as a joke, through the way 
that they left stubble on the transwoman's face and she did not pass very 
well. It probably would've been quite the same had it been a cisgender 
woman, but that shows that the adding of the trasgender trait was quite 
unnecessary and was clearly one of the jokes.

I like the video, it's funny, but I don't like the trans part, it makes me 
feel uncomfortable, as it feels like they are mocking trans people. I would 
have liked the video much better had the woman either not be trans or pass 
very well, because then that would eliminate the trans joke.
comments.author: Comrade Ogilvy

comments.text:

the fact that she's mentally unstable and a rapist that scares the man in 
this video so much. And that's where the comedy is derived from.
